==流行文化==
歌曲被形容为“海中的孤独岩石”，[[查尔斯·伯内特威尔逊|查尔斯·伯内特威尔逊]]回忆为“海边的岩石”并在1857年在其回忆录中出版，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://jscholarship.library.jhu.edu/handle/1774.2/22134 |title=The Rock Beside the Sea. A Romanza. |accessdate=2016-08-19 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304191401/https://jscholarship.library.jhu.edu/handle/1774.2/22134 |dead-url=no }}</ref>音乐学家[[Sigmund_Spaeth|Sigmund Spaeth]]指出，这首歌旋律的前两个小节（琶音IV-I和弦）<ref name="huapala" /> 很像{{le|乔治·弗雷德里克·鲁特|George Frederick Root}}在1854年所作的歌曲《There's Music In The Air》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://imslp.org/wiki/The_Story_of_a_Musical_Life_(Root,_George_Frederick) |title="The Story of a Musical Life," pp. 254-255 |accessdate=2016-08-19 |archive-date=2016-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919105740/http://imslp.org/wiki/The_Story_of_a_Musical_Life_(Root,_George_Frederick) |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在[[迪士尼|迪士尼]]电影《[[星际宝贝|星际宝贝]]》（2002年）中，这首歌由角色蘭莉简单地演唱。<ref>{{cite web|title=Lilo and Stich Aloha 'Oe|url=http://wn.com/lilo_and_stitch_aloha_'oe|publisher=wn.com|accessdate=2014-04-04|archive-date=2014-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610220711/http://wn.com/lilo_and_stitch_aloha_'oe|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Lilo and Stich Versions of Aloha Oe|url=http://theamazinghistoryofhawaii.weebly.com/aloha-oe.html|publisher=History of Hawaii|accessdate=2014-04-04|archive-date=2014-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407092121/http://theamazinghistoryofhawaii.weebly.com/aloha-oe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 这首歌也出现在电影的续集《星际宝贝 2：Island Favorites》的配乐中。<ref>{{cite web|last=Phares|first=Heather|title=Lilo & Stitch 2: Island Favorites|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/lilo-stitch-2-island-favorites-mw0000417489|publisher=All Music|accessdate=2014-04-04|archive-date=2015-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150104214357/http://www.allmusic.com/album/lilo-stitch-2-island-favorites-mw0000417489|dead-url=no}}</ref>

这首歌也多次在[[海绵宝宝|海绵宝宝]]的器乐演奏中出现。

在2014年日本动漫《[[宇宙浪子|宇宙浪子]]》中，主角驾驶的宇宙飞船同样也叫Aloha Oe<ref>{{cite web |last=Green |first=Scott |title=Figure Sculptor Makes "Space Dandy" Aloha Oe and QT |url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2014/01/24-1/figure-sculptor-makes-space-dandy-aloha-oe-and-qt |publisher=Crunchy Roll |accessdate=2014-04-04 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407082528/http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2014/01/24-1/figure-sculptor-makes-space-dandy-aloha-oe-and-qt |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Green |first=Victoria |title='Space Dandy' Recap: A Merry Companion Is a Wagon in Space, Baby |url=http://thecelebritycafe.com/feature/2014/02/space-dandy-recap-merry-companion-wagon-space-baby |publisher=The Celebrity Cafe |accessdate=2014-04-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407092548/http://thecelebritycafe.com/feature/2014/02/space-dandy-recap-merry-companion-wagon-space-baby |archivedate=2014-04-07 }}</ref>。

在[[杰克·伦敦|杰克·伦敦]]的短篇小说中，也出现了Aloha Oe这首歌的合唱<ref>{{cite book |last=London |first=Jack |title=The Complete Short Stories of Jack London, Volume 1 |url=http://books.google.es/books?id=xICaAAAAIAAJ&lpg=PA1473&dq=jack%20london%20aloha%20oe&pg=PA1474#v=onepage&q=onaona&f=false |publisher=Google Books |accessdate=2014-04-28 |archive-date=2014-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140428030759/http://books.google.es/books?id=xICaAAAAIAAJ&lpg=PA1473&dq=jack%20london%20aloha%20oe&pg=PA1474#v=onepage&q=onaona&f=false |dead-url=no }}。</ref>

{{Wikiquote|江泽民#在夏威夷演奏吉他}}
時任[[中华人民共和国最高领导人|中华人民共和国最高领导人]][[江泽民|江泽民]]于1997年10月到访夏威夷对美国进行国事访问时，在州长Ben Cayetano的晚宴上，他以[[钢棒吉他|钢棒吉他]]弹奏Aloha 'Oe（相关视频传播过程中，Aloha 'Oe曾被字幕错误地标注为Hello Hawaii）并邀请当时的州长夫人Vicky Cayetano演唱。据江泽民所述，他在20世纪40年代时曾频繁地演奏这首歌曲。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://partners.nytimes.com/library/world/102897us-china-jiang.1.jpg.html|title=President Jiang Zemin of China|website=partners.nytimes.com|access-date=2016-03-29|archive-date=2016-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130002356/https://partners.nytimes.com/library/world/102897us-china-jiang.1.jpg.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|last=StevenChangHZ|title=江澤民演奏夏威夷吉他[Jiang Zemin Playing Hawaiian Guitar]|date=2012-04-19|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1yQ5OxOXyi4|accessdate=2016-03-29|archive-date=2016-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160902030733/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1yQ5OxOXyi4|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2016年的韩国[[災難片|災難片电影]]中的《[[屍速列車|釜山行]]》最後片尾中，男主角徐碩宇的女儿徐秀安在[[隧道|隧道]]中大声唱出這首歌好讓[[军队|军队]]的[[狙擊手|狙擊手]]確認自己是沒有受到[[感染|感染]]的正常人，因此獲得軍隊的救援。

